Module de.sft.dlt
Package de.s42.dlt.parser.antlr

Interface DLTParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
DLTParserBaseListener, TemplateCompiler.ParserListener
public interface DLTParserListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by DLTParser.
